1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
(Watch on www.kisskh.li Support Admin)

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:08,160
Mr. Shen,

3
00:00:08,500 --> 00:00:10,380
I suppose you see Minghui's situation

4
00:00:10,420 --> 00:00:12,540
more clearly than I do.

5
00:00:12,740 --> 00:00:14,660
Miss Xu, have you decided

6
00:00:14,980 --> 00:00:16,500
to work with me?

7
00:00:17,540 --> 00:00:18,620
Mr. Shen,

8
00:00:20,220 --> 00:00:21,660
may I ask something a little bold?

9
00:00:24,780 --> 00:00:26,860
Can I marry you instead?

10
00:00:35,720 --> 00:00:41,399
=Echoes of Gang City=

11
00:00:41,400 --> 00:00:48,560
=Episode 1=
(Mr. Shen, Will You Say Yes?)

12
00:00:52,720 --> 00:00:53,729
(12 hours)

13
00:00:53,730 --> 00:00:54,539
Good morning,

14
00:00:54,540 --> 00:00:55,459
everyone.

15
00:00:55,460 --> 00:00:57,459
(Gang City Financial News)
Today is Tuesday, June 3rd.

16
00:00:57,460 --> 00:00:58,960
The eighth day of the fifth lunar month.

17
00:00:58,960 --> 00:01:01,459
Welcome to the morning
financial news program.

18
00:01:01,460 --> 00:01:02,970
I'm Xu Wanxin.

19
00:01:02,980 --> 00:01:05,660
First, here are today's top stories.

20
00:01:05,860 --> 00:01:07,619
A globally renowned group,

21
00:01:07,620 --> 00:01:09,619
Qingniao, has acquired land in Shanghai

22
00:01:09,620 --> 00:01:10,979
through its AI subsidiary.

23
00:01:10,980 --> 00:01:13,419
Qingniao Group has expanded its business

24
00:01:13,420 --> 00:01:14,940
by developing quantitative technologies.

25
00:01:15,380 --> 00:01:16,179
In just two years,

26
00:01:16,180 --> 00:01:18,380
it has become a global leader
in the industry.

27
00:01:18,820 --> 00:01:20,140
That's impressive.

28
00:01:20,740 --> 00:01:24,180
Minghui needs an investor like that.

29
00:01:24,780 --> 00:01:25,900
How is it?

30
00:01:25,940 --> 00:01:27,539
Have you found out

31
00:01:27,540 --> 00:01:29,220
who's behind Qingniao?

32
00:01:29,420 --> 00:01:31,019
We already have Junlin's investment,

33
00:01:31,020 --> 00:01:32,020
Mr. Hui.

34
00:01:36,260 --> 00:01:37,099
Dad.

35
00:01:37,100 --> 00:01:39,739
Why not have Wanxin and Shen Hao
get married as soon as possible?

36
00:01:39,740 --> 00:01:41,019
That would lock in the partnership.

37
00:01:41,020 --> 00:01:42,259
You can't even handle

38
00:01:42,260 --> 00:01:44,099
your own affairs,

39
00:01:44,100 --> 00:01:46,419
and now you're meddling
with Wanxin's marriage.

40
00:01:46,420 --> 00:01:47,499
Dad.

41
00:01:47,500 --> 00:01:48,780
Sit properly.

42
00:01:50,260 --> 00:01:51,540
Watch the news.

43
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:54,360
(Gang City Financial News)

44
00:01:56,780 --> 00:01:58,420
What's it? Why the rush?

45
00:01:58,660 --> 00:01:59,339
Ms. Xi,

46
00:01:59,340 --> 00:02:00,219
there's breaking news.

47
00:02:00,220 --> 00:02:01,300
You need to see this.

48
00:02:09,140 --> 00:02:10,439
This can't go on air.

49
00:02:10,440 --> 00:02:11,879
Ms. Xi, if we don't air it,

50
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:13,799
we might have a broadcast accident.

51
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:16,439
If there's an accident,
tell Madam Song to deal with me.

52
00:02:16,440 --> 00:02:18,519
Why are you still standing there?
Pull it down now.

53
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,640
Okay. I'll try.

54
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:30,600
Where's Aisen?

55
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:31,719
Is he here yet?

56
00:02:31,720 --> 00:02:33,279
Get him to replace Wanxin.

57
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:33,839
Hurry.

58
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,599
Jiang, switch the anchor. Go find Aisen.

59
00:02:35,600 --> 00:02:36,119
Now.

60
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,160
I'm going.

61
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:47,079
I can't. I don't have the authorization.
It's too late.

62
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:48,280
We can't remove it anymore.

63
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:49,399
Mr. Xu!

64
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,039
Dad!

65
00:02:50,040 --> 00:02:50,920
Mr. Xu!

66
00:02:51,080 --> 00:02:51,959
Dad!

67
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:54,039
Breaking news.

68
00:02:54,040 --> 00:02:57,199
CEO of Minghui Group,

69
00:02:57,200 --> 00:02:58,399
Mr. Xu Zhaoming,

70
00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:01,960
while on his way back
from Sun Valley Summit,

71
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:11,240
(was involved in a helicopter accident
and died)

72
00:03:16,880 --> 00:03:18,760
was involved

73
00:03:19,040 --> 00:03:20,159
in a helicopter accident

74
00:03:20,160 --> 00:03:21,140
and died

75
00:03:21,760 --> 00:03:23,050
at the age of 57.

76
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:41,559
I'm Song Xi.

77
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:42,799
Cut to the scene.

78
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:43,559
Change the anchor.

79
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:44,679
(Gang City Financial News)

80
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,479
Dear viewers,

81
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:47,079
I'm now at the crash site

82
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:48,879
on Sun Valley Mountain.

83
00:03:48,880 --> 00:03:49,919
As you can see,

84
00:03:49,920 --> 00:03:51,999
the area behind me has been sealed off,

85
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:54,079
and multiple rescue teams
are working at the scene.

86
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:54,879
As we're informed,

87
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:56,799
the helicopter
was carrying three people.

88
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:58,880
A pilot and two passengers.

89
00:03:58,920 --> 00:04:00,879
One of them has been confirmed

90
00:04:00,880 --> 00:04:02,039
as Xu Zhaoming,

91
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:03,559
President of Minghui Group,

92
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:06,459
who was here attending
the latest tech summit.

93
00:04:06,460 --> 00:04:07,979
Preliminary reports suggest

94
00:04:07,980 --> 00:04:11,189
the crash was caused by severe weather.

95
00:04:11,190 --> 00:04:14,270
The cause is still under investigation.

96
00:04:15,320 --> 00:04:15,959
Song Xi.

97
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:18,839
After Mr. Xu heard about Wanxin's dad's
accident, he suffered a heart attack.

98
00:04:18,840 --> 00:04:20,560
Get Wanxin back immediately.

99
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:21,880
Alright.

100
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:28,080
Wanxin.

101
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:30,640
Wanxin.

102
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:33,280
I know this is hard for you.

103
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:36,680
Dai Anna just called.

104
00:04:37,440 --> 00:04:40,040
Your grandfather heard the news
about your dad.

105
00:04:40,200 --> 00:04:41,760
He had a heart attack

106
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,640
and fainted.

107
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:53,359
Zhaohui,

108
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:55,720
I'm saddened by your brother's accident,

109
00:04:55,880 --> 00:04:57,879
but you must pull yourself together.

110
00:04:57,880 --> 00:05:01,680
This is your best chance
to take Minghui.

111
00:05:01,960 --> 00:05:03,439
No matter what it takes,

112
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:05,919
get Wanxin and Hao married
as soon as possible.

113
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:08,799
Hao will bring Junlin Group's
support and invest in Minghui

114
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:10,399
to stabilize the situation.

115
00:05:10,400 --> 00:05:11,439
At the same time,

116
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:14,120
we'll push you into
the chairman's seat.

117
00:05:20,420 --> 00:05:23,579
Today, Minghui Group President
Xu Zhaoming encountered a plane crash.

118
00:05:23,580 --> 00:05:26,739
Since the market opened,
Minghui's stock has taken a heavy hit.

119
00:05:26,740 --> 00:05:27,840
According to analysts,

120
00:05:27,840 --> 00:05:30,520
unless Junlin Group, which is tied
to Minghui by a marriage alliance,

121
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:31,749
steps in to help...

122
00:05:31,750 --> 00:05:33,320
If Shen Tingyuan

123
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:35,399
uses this chance

124
00:05:35,400 --> 00:05:37,600
to force Xu Wanxin to marry Shen Hao,

125
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:40,080
what should we do?

126
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:47,440
He won't get the chance.

127
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:54,959
How's my grandfather?

128
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:56,359
Wanxin, don't worry.

129
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:58,239
Dr. Zhang is with him.

130
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:59,400
He's stable for now.

131
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:05,159
Wanxin,

132
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:07,559
with what happened to
your grandfather and dad,

133
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:08,720
I know

134
00:06:09,080 --> 00:06:10,520
this is hard on you.

135
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:12,840
Right now, the family and the company

136
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:15,400
depend on us.

137
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:19,880
What's the situation at the company?

138
00:06:19,990 --> 00:06:21,440
The stock price is dropping.

139
00:06:21,880 --> 00:06:23,159
If the news of the chairman's coma

140
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:24,480
gets out,

141
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:26,960
and the price falls below 120,

142
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:28,560
Datong Bank

143
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:30,560
will call in the loans.

144
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:35,600
It's fine.

145
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:38,239
Junlin Group is tied to us
through the marriage alliance.

146
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,920
As long as they step in,

147
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:43,320
everything will be resolved.

148
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:46,800
Uncle Zhaohui,

149
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:50,399
shouldn't we try to
handle this ourselves first?

150
00:06:50,400 --> 00:06:53,319
Xu Wanxin, do you really think
being the Xu family's daughter

151
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:54,999
and a finance anchor

152
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:57,560
is enough to bring in
funding and resources?

153
00:06:58,640 --> 00:07:00,079
Your most valuable identity

154
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:01,719
is being Shen Hao's fiancée.

155
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:03,479
What you should do now

156
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,679
is call Shen Hao

157
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:06,520
and set the wedding date.

158
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,720
A woman

159
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,640
needs to know when to show weakness.

160
00:07:13,080 --> 00:07:14,840
That's how you save the Xu family.

161
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,600
I understand your concern.

162
00:07:21,880 --> 00:07:23,240
If necessary,

163
00:07:23,640 --> 00:07:26,360
I can mortgage my personal assets.

164
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:31,480
Please keep our conversation

165
00:07:32,200 --> 00:07:33,720
confidential.

166
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:20,120
Excuse me.

167
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,840
You are?

168
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,320
I'm Shen Gu.

169
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:33,560
I heard about what happened to Mr. Xu,

170
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:35,240
so I came to see you...

171
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:38,760
To see

172
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:41,080
if there's anything I can help with.

173
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:43,640
Mr. Shen,

174
00:08:44,520 --> 00:08:45,720
I'm sorry

175
00:08:46,280 --> 00:08:47,480
I didn't recognize you

176
00:08:47,520 --> 00:08:48,800
after all these years.

177
00:08:52,760 --> 00:08:54,760
Thank you for your concern
for my dad.

178
00:08:55,920 --> 00:08:56,759
I appreciate it.

179
00:08:56,760 --> 00:08:57,880
Miss Xu.

180
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:03,959
(Shen Gu)

181
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:05,880
Since you remember who I am,

182
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:06,999
you should know

183
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,720
why I've returned to Gang City.

184
00:09:09,400 --> 00:09:11,159
I know about your engagement
to Shen Hao,

185
00:09:11,160 --> 00:09:14,000
and I'm well aware
of Minghui's current situation.

186
00:09:14,800 --> 00:09:17,640
What happened between Junlin and me
in the past may drag your family into it.

187
00:09:17,680 --> 00:09:19,880
So I hope you'll break off
the engagement

188
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:21,760
and choose to work with me.

189
00:09:24,800 --> 00:09:26,640
You don't have to refuse right away.

190
00:09:27,040 --> 00:09:28,600
Think it over.

191
00:09:28,910 --> 00:09:30,400
We can talk anytime.

192
00:09:32,560 --> 00:09:34,000
Thank you again for your concern.

193
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:08,160
It's been so many years.

194
00:10:08,880 --> 00:10:10,280
It's only natural for her

195
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:12,320
to be cautious.

196
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:16,640
Li Yan and you will handle

197
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:18,760
Qingniao's investment in Minghui.

198
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:21,520
Have our people contact
Xu Wanxin directly.

199
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:23,160
No one

200
00:10:23,740 --> 00:10:27,600
is allowed to delay the process under the excuse
of Mr. Xu Zhaoming's death.

201
00:10:28,640 --> 00:10:29,960
Next,

202
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:33,560
it's time we meet Shen Tingyuan.

203
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:49,080
We need to keep the initiative
in our hands.

204
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:50,879
Release the news

205
00:10:50,880 --> 00:10:52,639
that Xu Qiaomo is seriously ill

206
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:54,119
and force Minghui.

207
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:57,159
Don't give Xu Wanxin any room to stall.

208
00:10:57,160 --> 00:10:59,760
This time, I'm taking
Minghui completely.

209
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:07,879
Hello?

210
00:11:07,880 --> 00:11:09,040
Mr. Tingyuan,

211
00:11:09,520 --> 00:11:11,119
our boss has arrived in Gang City.

212
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:13,400
He requests a meeting
with your entire board.

213
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:15,760
I'll arrange it.

214
00:11:16,100 --> 00:11:18,160
Welcome to Gang City.

215
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:22,760
He says,

216
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:25,840
"Welcome to Gang City."

217
00:12:27,480 --> 00:12:29,640
Is he coming or not?

218
00:12:29,920 --> 00:12:31,840
If this delays plans with Xu Wanxin,

219
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:33,159
who's taking responsibility?

220
00:12:33,160 --> 00:12:34,799
Mr. Shen, calm down.

221
00:12:34,800 --> 00:12:36,919
Xu Wanxin is yours.

222
00:12:36,920 --> 00:12:38,040
Don't make me laugh.

223
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:40,240
Who in Gang City

224
00:12:40,320 --> 00:12:41,520
would dare take her from me?

225
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:43,840
What if I do?

226
00:12:59,920 --> 00:13:01,360
Shen Tingyuan,

227
00:13:01,920 --> 00:13:03,520
after all these years,

228
00:13:03,760 --> 00:13:05,520
you don't even recognize me?

229
00:13:16,280 --> 00:13:17,720
Shen Gu?

230
00:13:19,080 --> 00:13:20,399
Why did you take me here?

231
00:13:20,400 --> 00:13:23,159
I won't let you ruin my reputation
in Gang City.

232
00:13:23,160 --> 00:13:24,680
Wasn't it enough
that you caused my mom's death?

233
00:13:24,680 --> 00:13:25,959
She brought it on herself.

234
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:28,280
Didn't you think you were capable?

235
00:13:31,840 --> 00:13:33,320
Live well, then.

236
00:13:33,680 --> 00:13:36,720
I'll be waiting for your return.

237
00:13:43,040 --> 00:13:44,400
So

238
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:47,240
you bought the Jinzhao Tower?

239
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:48,920
That's right.

240
00:13:50,720 --> 00:13:52,080
Mr. Shen Gu

241
00:13:52,160 --> 00:13:55,199
not only bought back
his late father's company building,

242
00:13:55,200 --> 00:13:56,799
but he also holds

243
00:13:56,800 --> 00:13:58,640
35% of Junlin Group shares

244
00:13:58,920 --> 00:14:02,600
and is currently
its largest shareholder.

245
00:14:02,720 --> 00:14:04,040
This is hilarious.

246
00:14:04,960 --> 00:14:07,040
You left with nothing.

247
00:14:07,160 --> 00:14:09,240
Now you wave some fake documents

248
00:14:09,280 --> 00:14:10,720
in my face?

249
00:14:12,600 --> 00:14:13,840
Sorry.

250
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:18,160
Our legal team doesn't deal
with anything illegal.

251
00:14:29,320 --> 00:14:32,120
Suspend all cooperation regarding Shen.

252
00:14:32,640 --> 00:14:33,720
Yes.

253
00:14:34,200 --> 00:14:35,360
All of them.

254
00:14:46,760 --> 00:14:47,959
Hello?

255
00:14:47,960 --> 00:14:48,960
What?

256
00:14:49,080 --> 00:14:50,360
Stop all cooperation immediately.

257
00:14:50,640 --> 00:14:51,560
We've received notice

258
00:14:51,560 --> 00:14:53,760
that we must stop all business
with the Shen family at once.

259
00:14:53,760 --> 00:14:55,240
Nonsense!

260
00:14:57,280 --> 00:14:58,840
Take your time to check it.

261
00:14:58,960 --> 00:15:01,600
As the largest shareholder
of Junlin Group,

262
00:15:01,720 --> 00:15:05,280
I'm calling for a shareholders' meeting
to replace the chairman.

263
00:15:05,760 --> 00:15:09,080
This is my welcome gift.

264
00:15:17,400 --> 00:15:19,960
You think replacing the chairman

265
00:15:20,760 --> 00:15:22,960
is something you,

266
00:15:23,840 --> 00:15:26,520
who has no footing on the board,
can decide?

267
00:15:37,520 --> 00:15:38,600
Why don't you guess

268
00:15:39,920 --> 00:15:41,040
who our footing

269
00:15:41,160 --> 00:15:42,960
here is?

270
00:16:05,520 --> 00:16:07,279
Madam Song just informed me

271
00:16:07,280 --> 00:16:08,839
that someone named Shen Gu

272
00:16:08,840 --> 00:16:10,279
has just called a Junlin board meeting

273
00:16:10,280 --> 00:16:12,519
as the largest shareholder

274
00:16:12,520 --> 00:16:14,639
and is requesting
to replace the chairman.

275
00:16:14,640 --> 00:16:15,960
Shen Gu?

276
00:16:16,760 --> 00:16:18,920
Is it the one I'm thinking of?

277
00:16:19,080 --> 00:16:20,159
Madam Song said

278
00:16:20,160 --> 00:16:22,840
he has a personal feud
with Shen Tingyuan.

279
00:16:24,080 --> 00:16:25,960
Since you remember who I am,

280
00:16:26,080 --> 00:16:28,480
you should know
why I've returned to Gang City.

281
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:31,079
I know about your engagement
to Shen Hao

282
00:16:31,080 --> 00:16:33,840
and I'm well aware
of Minghui's current situation.

283
00:16:34,760 --> 00:16:37,240
I don't want Junlin's affairs
to drag your family down.

284
00:16:37,640 --> 00:16:39,800
So I hope you'll break off
the engagement

285
00:16:40,160 --> 00:16:41,600
and choose to work with me.

286
00:16:43,800 --> 00:16:46,040
(Shen Gu)

287
00:16:51,400 --> 00:16:54,280
(Xu Wanxin)

288
00:16:58,960 --> 00:17:00,080
Hello?

289
00:17:00,600 --> 00:17:01,919
Hello, Mr. Shen.

290
00:17:01,920 --> 00:17:03,279
This is Xu Wanxin.

291
00:17:03,280 --> 00:17:04,880
Can we meet?

292
00:17:07,320 --> 00:17:08,480
Mr. Shen,

293
00:17:09,080 --> 00:17:10,240
sorry to trouble you.

294
00:17:10,720 --> 00:17:12,600
I suppose you see Minghui's situation

295
00:17:12,840 --> 00:17:14,800
more clearly than I do.

296
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:18,079
I know Shen Tingyuan

297
00:17:18,080 --> 00:17:19,920
has released news
that Mr. Xu is seriously ill.

298
00:17:20,480 --> 00:17:22,400
He's determined

299
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:24,160
to take over Minghui.

300
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:27,480
He won't stop.

301
00:17:30,600 --> 00:17:32,320
Miss Xu, have you decided

302
00:17:32,640 --> 00:17:34,200
to work with me?

303
00:17:34,680 --> 00:17:35,719
Mr. Shen,

304
00:17:35,720 --> 00:17:37,240
may I ask something a little bold?

305
00:17:37,560 --> 00:17:38,840
Do you have a girlfriend

306
00:17:39,280 --> 00:17:40,840
or partner?

307
00:17:50,280 --> 00:17:51,240
I'm single.

308
00:17:56,800 --> 00:17:58,320
My dad is gone.

309
00:17:58,560 --> 00:17:59,760
My grandfather is unconscious.

310
00:18:00,640 --> 00:18:03,000
Only a marriage alliance
between Minghui and Junlin

311
00:18:03,400 --> 00:18:05,360
can restore confidence in the market.

312
00:18:06,160 --> 00:18:08,000
But if I marry Shen Hao,

313
00:18:08,280 --> 00:18:09,480
Minghui

314
00:18:10,040 --> 00:18:12,240
will fall into Shen Tingyuan's hands.

315
00:18:13,400 --> 00:18:14,960
I have to protect the company.

316
00:18:15,760 --> 00:18:17,840
It's my grandfather and dad's
life's work.

317
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:20,080
And you

318
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:24,720
are now the largest shareholder
of Junlin Group.

319
00:18:26,040 --> 00:18:27,120
So

320
00:18:31,400 --> 00:18:34,120
can I marry you instead?

321
00:18:46,880 --> 00:18:47,960
Xu Wanxin,

322
00:18:49,400 --> 00:18:51,600
do you realize what you're saying?

323
00:18:53,160 --> 00:18:54,479
I'll give you

324
00:18:54,480 --> 00:18:55,880
Minghui's key projects

325
00:18:56,000 --> 00:18:58,200
so you can use them as leverage
against Shen Tingyuan.

326
00:18:59,560 --> 00:19:01,720
You're the largest shareholder of Junlin.

327
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:03,120
If we marry,

328
00:19:03,800 --> 00:19:06,080
it'll stabilize the stock price quickly.

329
00:19:06,160 --> 00:19:08,080
It's a win-win.

330
00:19:12,240 --> 00:19:13,360
Shen Gu,

331
00:19:15,920 --> 00:19:18,000
will you consider my proposal?

332
00:19:42,480 --> 00:19:45,240
(Gang City Marriage Registry)

333
00:20:12,930 --> 00:20:18,720
♪Tonight the rain falls soft and slow♪

334
00:20:20,000 --> 00:20:25,800
♪Blending with letters left unread
drifting through the air♪

335
00:20:26,500 --> 00:20:31,890
♪You turn and look back at me♪

336
00:20:33,010 --> 00:20:38,500
♪In those same eyes familiar tears
quietly appear♪

337
00:20:39,360 --> 00:20:45,010
♪It feels like we have carried so much♪

338
00:20:46,290 --> 00:20:51,750
♪So many questions time itself
could not make clear♪

339
00:20:52,870 --> 00:20:58,190
♪The moment you walked into my life♪

340
00:20:59,340 --> 00:21:05,170
♪Every dream I had became something
I want with you near♪

341
00:21:05,540 --> 00:21:12,510
♪How many letters have I written
just for you?♪

342
00:21:12,620 --> 00:21:18,330
♪If only you could truly hear
what my heart is trying to say♪

343
00:21:18,990 --> 00:21:25,359
♪From this life on no distance
could keep us apart♪

344
00:21:25,360 --> 00:21:28,239
♪The promise we made♪

345
00:21:28,240 --> 00:21:31,929
♪Will find its way to be fulfilled
one day♪

346
00:21:31,930 --> 00:21:38,509
♪But I want more
than just that fleeting gaze♪

347
00:21:38,510 --> 00:21:44,920
♪Still I have not heard your answer♪

348
00:21:45,310 --> 00:21:51,649
♪Can we still rewrite the ending
we face?♪

349
00:21:51,650 --> 00:21:56,740
♪When regrets begin to turn around you
will hear it all♪

350
00:21:57,220 --> 00:22:00,240
♪Everything that leads me back to you♪
